conda create --name transformer python=3.10
conda activate transformer


conda install conda-forge::scanpy
conda install conda-forge::transformers


========================================
Transporter Gene Databases
Transporter Classification Database (TCDB):
	•	A curated database of transporters classified into functional families.
HUGO Gene Nomenclature Committee (HGNC) - Transporter Genes:
	•	Provides a standard list of human transporter genes.
Gene Ontology (GO) Annotations for Transporters:
	•	Use GO terms like: GO:0005215 (Transporter activity) GO:0015932 (Nucleotide transport) GO:0006810 (Transport)

